About Us

Welcome to Saar Biotech

Saar Biotech Pvt. Ltd., a distinguished and WHO-GMP certified third-party pharmaceutical manufacturing company. Since our establishment in 2005, we have been operating from our state-of-the-art manufacturing unit in Baddi, complemented by our centrally located head office in Chandigarh.
